32:21.106 --> 32:22.572
(laughter)

32:22.574 --> 32:24.875
Lucious's music took the street

32:24.877 --> 32:27.311
mainstream, and made
the mainstream feel street.

32:27.313 --> 32:29.613
Everything Lucious touches

32:29.615 --> 32:32.316
