36:54.213 --> 36:56.880
Amyotrophic
Lateral Sclerosis.

36:56.882 --> 36:58.381
It is a...

36:58.383 --> 37:00.150
(sighs)

37:00.152 --> 37:01.818
...an aggressive

37:01.820 --> 37:03.687
and degenerative

37:03.689 --> 37:05.589
